{"article_id":"2JMRa5OSUsSG1l8W","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump threatened to shut down the government during a heated argument with Democratic congressional leaders in the Oval Office on Tuesday in a remarkable display of partisan bickering","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"just 10 days before a partial shutdown is set to take effect .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"\" I am proud to shut down the government for border security , \"","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Trump said bluntly .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" I will take the mantle .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"I will be the one","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"to shut it down .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"I ' m not going to blame you for it .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The last time","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"you shut it down ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"it didn ' t work .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"I will take the mantle","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"of shutting down .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"And I ' m going to shut it down for border security . \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"The remark came during an extraordinary 15-minute on-camera argument","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that began","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"with Trump insisting","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"should help him fund a border wall .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Trump has asked for $ 5 billion in border-security funding ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"but Democrats have said","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"$ 1.6 billion is their red line .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"At first , both leaders sat silently","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"listening to Trump read dubious figures and repeat falsehoods","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"about how much of the wall has already been built .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"When Pelosi reminded the president","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"that he does not have enough votes in the House","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to fund it ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"the president pivoted","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"and began boasting about his party ' s electoral gains in the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" When the president brags","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"that he won North Dakota and Indiana ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"he ' s in real trouble , \"","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Schumer said with a laugh .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"An exasperated Pelosi repeated to Trump","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that he does not have enough votes among House Republicans alone","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"to fully fund a border wall ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and Trump responded","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"by saying","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"he needs 60 votes in the Senate ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"where Republicans have just a 51-to-49 majority ,","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"to get anything to his desk .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" The fact is , you do not have the votes in the House , \"","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Pelosi said ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to which Trump insisted :","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"\" Nancy , I do . \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Schumer then confronted Trump directly over his exaggerations and mistruths about the border wall .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" We have a lot of disagreements here .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"The Washington Post today gave you a whole lot of Pinocchios","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"because they say","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"you constantly misstate","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"how much of the wall is built , \"","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"a defiant Schumer said .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"\" You have called 20 times","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to shut down the government .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"You say ,","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"' I want to shut down the government. '","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"We don ' t .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"We want to come to an agreement . \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"At one point , Trump jabbed at Pelosi ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"\" Nancy ' s in a situation","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"where it ' s not easy for her to talk right now . \"","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Pelosi fired back immediately ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"telling the president ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"\" Please don ' t characterize the strength","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"that I bring to this meeting","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"as leader of the House Democrats","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"who just won a big victory . \"","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"After the meeting , Schumer vented about the president ' s tone during the sit-down .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" This temper tantrum","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that he seems to throw","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"will not get him his wall , \"","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"The partisan jabbing ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"which came during a photo opportunity","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"before Trump was set to negotiate with Pelosi and Schumer behind closed doors ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"represented a preview of what to expect with a divided government next year ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"when Democrats officially take control of the House of Representatives .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" Unfortunately , this has spiraled downward","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"when we came at a place","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"to say ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"how do we meet the needs of the American people , \"","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":4},{"id":87,"text":"During the tense exchanges , Vice President Mike Pence sat stoically next to Trump","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"and remained silent .","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"After the meeting , some Republicans began rallying behind the president .","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"( R-SC ) ,","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"a Trump ally , tweeted ,","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"\" Great job sticking to your guns on border security , Mr. President !","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"You are right","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"to want more border security funding","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"including Wall money .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"They are WRONG","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"to say no . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":197,"left":185,"right":196,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":123,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":100,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":111,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":101,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":107,"right":109,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":104,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":103,"right":7,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":4,"right":102,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":102,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":13,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":118,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":14,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclear